	   <tr><td colspan=2>The previous poster is completely wrong. You can create a pet higher than a blue after 16.&nbsp;&nbsp;Not only that, but I created a pet that coned even to me at 20 or 21 (cant remember which).  But, it is VERY rare.  That was the first pet to con even to me since my early teens.  I dont know if you can ever get one that cons even after the 20's though.  I have noted that since I have been in my 20's, I have produced no green pets, though I dont know if I am just lucky or not.<br>As for the "shovel, torch, mug, broom" the poster mentions, those are what are called focus items.  They do boost your pets hit points, but don't jump out of your seat just yet, as they don't affect your pets until level 34.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
