	   <tr><td colspan=2>Just wanted to make a note:<br>ALL lvl 16 & lvl 20 spells are located on a vendor on the OOT island, just after Sister Island. You have to swim to it, but never fear, no dangerous creatures live in the waters here.<br>Besides, you can always use a benefit to your swimming skill, hehe :)&nbsp;&nbsp;Careful on the island, though, as occasionally cyclops spawn there. Invis yourself!  The vendor is in the tower at the very top of the mountain. <br>GOOD LUCK!<br><br>Almythea<br>Magician of the 17th Element<br>Servant of Karana<br>Prexus<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
