	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well, there are a few places you can look. One is on the Ocean of Tears, bewtween Freport and Kaladim, where there is a tower on an island (shout when you land, someone will direct you) - they sell quite a few spells. Remember to bind back in one of the city zones, so you can Gate back. <br><br>There are also the libraries in Ak'Anon, Erudin or Neriak (if you are evil class). Try there. <br><br>After level 24 you'll have to research most of your spells, so get those points into research now!<br><br>Hannaye (Bertoloxx)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
